Sentencas: The mechanical properties, such as Young's modulus, Vickers hardness, indentation fracture resistance, room and high temperature four-point bending strength and SEVNB fracture toughness along with the stress-strain deformation behavior in compression, of 10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-ZrO2 (ScCeZrO2) ceramics have been studied.
Titulo: Mechanical properties of 10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-89 mol% ZrO2 ceramics

Sentencas: The chosen composition of the ScCeZrO2 has very high ionic conductivity and, therefore, is very promising oxygen ion conducting electrolyte for the intermediate temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Mechanical properties of 10 mol% Sc2O3-1 mol% CeO2-89 mol% ZrO2 ceramics

Sentencas: Therefore, its mechanical behavior is of importance and is presented in the paper.
